{"tid":2091524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民族無產階級！聯合起來反抗資本主義吧！","createTime":"2020-07-02T17:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T04:03:32.000Z","uid":259812,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1394a2838ebb01e60437485a3a0efdcdd06dd1","tid":2091524,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"香港人的暴力革命是無產階級聯合起來反抗資本主義，歷史主義的必然進程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n階級鬥爭和當中的暴力是必然的，香港人以武抗暴打倒資本主義才是最值得中國十四億人驕傲的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想不到在香港回歸祖國後資本主義仍未褪色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一國兩制的資本主義簡直是把開國先父們教誨置諸腦後的奇恥大辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如今香港民族！無產階級！聯合起來反抗資本主義吧！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xp8tH3z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXp8tH3z.jpg&h=00874a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NwUky8R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNwUky8R.jpg&h=47806836&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3a9fc01aa4313ec933b18bbae06bdc4d4ce58db","tid":2091524,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"打倒資本主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4065a4d8f3cfa80f5b34876085141d80b9d94de8","tid":2091524,"uid":259812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T17:05:11.000Z","msg":"P牌推到資本主義倒台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4a49a2c48e0faeee866f05740c1f3fd40ea0d5","tid":2091524,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"推倒資本主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9449fbaf8f9b9d